NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A. Key Developments

NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A., Q2 2017 Earnings Call, Jul 21, 2017
Jul 20 17
NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A., Q2 2017 Earnings Call, Jul 21, 2017


NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A. Announces Consolidated Earnings Results for the Second Quarter of 2017
Jul 20 17
NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A. announced consolidated earnings results for the second quarter of 2017. For the quarter, the revenues grew by EUR 15.6 million, equal to an increase of 4.2%, compared to the second quarter of 2016, as a result of continuous growth in services, while EBITDA increased by 5.4% to EUR 156.7 million. Consolidated Net Profit grew by EUR 13.9 million to reach a total of EUR 40.4 million, reflecting the positive contribution from affiliated companies. Free Cash Flow totalled EUR 43.9 million. Capital Expenditure (total CAPEX) was EUR 85.7 million.


