Is the PEG ratio within a reasonable range (0 to 1)? (1 check)
Is the PB ratio less than the Media industry average (and greater than 0)? (1 check)
NOS S.G.P.S. S.A has a total score of 3/6, see the detailed checks below.
Note: We use GAAP Earnings per Share in all our calculations including PE and PEG Ratio.
Note 2: PEG ratio is based on analysts EPS growth expectations in 1 year (16%).
