Company News







Company Info
Description








NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A. offers integrated telecommunications services worldwide. It operates through Telco and Audiovisuals segments. The company offers fixed and mobile solutions for television, Internet, voice, and data for residential, personal, business, and wholesale markets, as well as pay TV, next generation broadband, and cinema distribution and exhibition services. It also provides content; manages and acquires rights; and distributes movies and series. The company distributes its products to cinema, home entertainment, and TV platforms. In addition, it engages in content exhibition in movie theatres; operating as a programming aggregator on a linear and non-linear model, providing channels and services to other operators; managing a pay TV advertising business under the NOS Publicidade brand; selling advertising space; and providing advertising solutions, such as product placement, sponsoring, and complementary online presence related with content wholesale. Further, the company designs, constructs, and manages electronic communications networks, and equipment and infrastructures; and installs and manages towers and other sites for the roll-out of telecommunications equipment. Additionally, it manages real estate properties; commercializes other public events; offers consulting services in the area of information systems; owns intellectual property; provides electronic communications services and equipment; promotes scientific research and development activities; imports, distributes, commercializes, and produces audiovisual products; and purchases, sells, and rents property. It also engages in the realization of urbanization and building construction, planning, urban management, studies, construction and property management, and buy and sale of properties. NOS, S.G.P.S., S.A. has a strategic partnership with Huawei. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Lisbon, Portugal. NOS, SGPS, S.A. is a subsidiary of ZOPT, SGPS, S.A.


